title: #92Noon! Russo/Snob/BJ/Harris/Gene/Clomp
description: Full show! Russo kicks things off with Wild intel, Stump the Snob, Brad Johnson joins for Super Bowl stories, Ryan Harris won a super bowl with the Broncos and joins midway thru, Gene Deckerhoff starts final hour as he preps to call his 2nd SB for the Bucs, Ryan Cardinal's country clompfest for Gophers hockey, and SuperBowl 55 talkers to wrap!
